      "value": "<style>\n.thick-table table {\n  border-collapse: separate;\n  border-spacing: 0;\n  border: 2px solid black !important;\n  background-color: #f5f5f5;\n}\n\n.thick-table th,\n.thick-table td {\n  padding: 8px 10px !important;\n  border: 1px solid black;\n  font-size: 14px;\n}\n\n.thick-table th {\n  background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);\n  font-weight: 600;\n}\n\n/* Alternating row colors */\n.thick-table tbody tr:nth-child(even) {\n  background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.02);\n}\n\n.thick-table tbody tr:nth-child(odd) {\n  background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);\n}\n\n/* Ensure header row maintains its styling */\n.thick-table thead tr {\n  background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05) !important;\n}\n</style>\n\n<div class=\"alert alert-info\" style=\"color: black;\">\n<h4><b>Activity 4.3: Display the Counts</b></h4>\n\nStart this activity by navigating to <a href=\"../ui/c3/src/customInstances/Aircraft.BaseDetailsPage.tsx\" style=\"color: blue;\">/ui/c3/src/customInstances/Aircraft.BaseDetailsPage.tsx</a>.\n\n**Instructions**:\n\n1. Open the file `Aircraft.BaseDetailsPage.tsx`.\n2. Import the `KPIStatsContainer` and `KPIStatsTile` components from `/components/stats/` in `TODO 4.3.1`.\n3. Add the components to the page's rendered JSX in `TODO 4.3.2`:\n</div>",
