    {
      "kind": 1,
      "languageId": "markdown",
      "value": "---\n\n## Part 5: Complete the `Aircraft` Paginated Table Component\n\nIn the final section, you'll complete the dashboard by displaying all of the `Aircraft` Types located at the `Base`.\n\nDue to the size of the `Aircraft` records, we need to fetch the records 10 at a time, on demand.\n\nIn this section, you'll implement a production-grade paginated table that:\n- Loads data in manageable chunks.\n- Lets users page through results smoothly.\n- Keeps the interface fast.",
      "output": [],
      "executionSummary": {}
    },
    {
      "kind": 1,
      "languageId": "markdown",
      "value": "<div class=\"alert alert-info\" style=\"color: black;\">\n<h4><b>Activity 5.1: Retrieve the Aircraft Data with Pagination</b></h4>\n\nStart this activity by navigating to <a href=\"../ui/c3/src/components/CRUDMethods/AircraftCRUD.ts\" style=\"color: blue;\">/ui/c3/src/components/CRUDMethods/AircraftCRUD.ts</a>.\n\n**Instructions**:\n\n1. Open the file `AircraftCRUD.ts`.\n2. Complete `TODO 5.1` in the function `fetchAircraftWithPagination`:\n\n    i. Make a `POST` request to the endpoint `api/8/Aircraft/fetch`.\n    \n    - Use the `fetch()` API with method `POST`.\n    - Include headers: `{ 'Content-Type': 'application/json' }`.\n    - Pass a request body that filters the `Aircraft` by `Base` ID, limits the response to `pageSize`, and includes the `offset`.\n        - **Hint**: The fetch spec parameters can be seen in the <a href=\"https://docs.c3.ai/docs/platform/8.8/type/FetchSpec\" style=\"color: blue;\">FetchSpec Type Documentation</a>.\n\n    ii. Parse the response as JSON.\n\n    iii. Return the parsed data.",
      "output": [],
      "executionSummary": {}
    },
    {
      "kind": 1,
      "languageId": "markdown",
      "value": "Next, we need to call the function in the paginated aircraft table component.",
      "output": [],
      "executionSummary": {}
    },
    {
      "kind": 1,
      "languageId": "markdown",
      "value": "<div class=\"alert alert-info\" style=\"color: black;\">\n<h4><b>Activity 5.2: Trigger the API Call</b></h4>\n\nStart this activity by navigating to <a href=\"../ui/c3/src/components/table/AircraftPaginatedTable.tsx\" style=\"color: blue;\">/ui/c3/src/components/table/AircraftPaginatedTable.tsx</a>.\n\n**Instructions**:\n\n1. Open the file `AircraftPaginatedTable.tsx`.\n2. Import the function `fetchAircraftWithPagination` from the file `AircraftCRUD.ts` in `TODO 5.2.1`.\n3. Complete `TODO 5.2.2` in the `useEffect` hook:\n    - Call the function `fetchAircraftWithPagination` passing in the `PAGE_SIZE` as the `pageSize` and `page * PAGE_SIZE` as the offset.\n    - Store the JSON response into the `aircraftData` state.\n</div>",
