    {
      "kind": 1,
      "languageId": "markdown",
      "value": "<div class=\"alert alert-info\" style=\"color: black;\">\n<h4><b>Activity 5.3: Display the Paginated Table</b></h4>\n\nStart this activity by navigating to <a href=\"../ui/c3/src/customInstances/Aircraft.BaseDetailsPage.tsx\" style=\"color: blue;\">/ui/c3/src/customInstances/Aircraft.BaseDetailsPage.tsx</a>.\n\n**Instructions**:\n\n1. Open the file `Aircraft.BaseDetailsPage.tsx`.\n2. Import the `AircraftPaginatedTable` component from `AircraftPaginatedTable.tsx` in `TODO 5.3.1`.\n3. Add the component to the page's JSX in `TODO 5.3.2`:",
      "output": [],
