      "value": "### Check Your Work\n\n**Expected Behavior**:\n\nNavigate to a `Base` details page and scroll to the bottom to see:\n\n1. A table displaying 10 aircraft records with columns:\n    - ID\n    - Model\n    - Registration Number\n    - Status\n2. Pagination controls at the bottom\n3. Page numbers\n4. Ability to click the right arrow (`>`) to load more aircraft.\n\n\nBy the end of this activity, you should be able to:\n1. Navigate to the `Base` details page for a `Base`.\n2. Render all the `Aircraft` Types at that `Base` in a paginated table.",
